    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, and it\u2019s been kept tucked away in a garage to keep it looking perfect. The interior is still sparkling and it drives like an absolute dream. You won't find one better cared for than this! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 44900.0,
