    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46), a masterclass in naturally aspirated performance. This specimen features the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double-VANOS system for razor-sharp throttle response and a linear 8,000 RPM powerband. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque vectoring. The chassis is in flawless condition, with proactive subframe reinforcement and factory-spec bushings maintaining original kinematic integrity. Finished with impeccable paint depth and a pristine interior, this M3 offers the tactile feedback and mechanical purity that defines the golden era of the M division.",
